    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 Each round begins on the main game board, where players take turns rolling dice to move or spending coins earned from minigames to gain advantages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 With over 16 minigames, there's something for everyone. Some are solo, others in teams, compete in a rotating lineup of unique and action-packed challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👑 Every minigame is a chance to collect coins and win a crown. Use those coins to gain an edge: add a whole extra die to your toss, teleport to any other player's board position, or skip someone’s turn by trapping them in a cage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for get-togethers, holidays, and game nights with friends: <i>Couch Party</i> is a game for everyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
